reviewText: He was my favorite actor. I like all his movies that I have seen

I read where Audie got tired of making the westerns but he was so great in them because he was so believable in the roles.  He just seemed so authentic. He could do all that fancy shooting, riding, and fighting in real life and was the real deal.  I love all of his movies and respect him as the most decorated soldier in US military history.  His true life story is remarkable.

Im a fan of westerns an Audie Murphy westerns . I see alot coming on cable perhaps 3-4 times a week . I saw its on this friday at 4 in the morning . Im lucky to own a DVD recorder to tape this movie .

This is another Audie Murphy classic the story line is
great plenty of action if you are a avid western movie
fan then i would recommend this highly. The service from
RareWaves in the UK was great communication excellent
would recommend this supplier.
In my opinion Audie Murphy can do no wrong and this is another example of his excellent work even though many people say he couldn't act.
